<div class="panel panel-info">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h3 class="panel-title">PT MACS Manual</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="panel-body">
   <ul class="list-group">
  	<li class="list-group-item">The Physical Therapist Manual for the Assessment of Clinical Skills (PT MACS) is a clinical skills assessment document that has been developed by clinical and academic faculty. Its format is similar to The Blue MACS, an assessment tool in use since 1977. A task force comprised of ACCEs, DCEs and clinicians was charged with developing the content and format of the new PT MACS. (Former users of The Blue MACS click here (http://www.texasconsortium.org/ptmacs_instructions.htm) for differences between the two evaluation tools.)</li>
   </ul>
  </div>
</div>

